column5: May the fourth be with you. Happy Star Wars day! Hope y'all have a great weekend.
And also with you. Time to start planting something . . .
Same to you Roy.  Looking like a fine day for Juli and I to have our first go at fishing out of kayaks. May the fourth be with us, lol!
Yeah, I have 100' of fence to plant today.
You and Juli have a great time on the water, Frankie. Get some pics...I wanna see Juli get a 54" incidental muskie in the kayak!
Perfect weather in the N.Bay today... low winds, high sun, my canoe is calling...AP here I come.
Same to you Roy.  I've got 7 patio stones to lay today and a cabana to set up out back.  Looks like some lovely weather to do it in
and if I may I ask, what you harvest from that fence?
